{
  "stem": "23626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember one incident where I was trembling, and my teeth were jittering it was so cold.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I looked up in the grey sky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[CRYING] And I thanked God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I thanked God that my mother was spared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was so cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we also saw people in Auschwitz, other women, that must have been there a long time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They looked so dreadful in those tattered clothes, in this shabby clothes, so skinny, with shaven heads.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Sometimes they would steal this little soupy cereal, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was like-- they gave us like a watery cereal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was like water, practically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They would grab from us, they were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I guess they couldn't control them self.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And some times later, I heard some of our-- of the 300 people-- would say, you know, maybe this is what's going to happen when we, when we remain here longer.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I always kept saying, Schindler would do something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Schindler would do-- but, naturally, you could never tell what can happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The three weeks were, were very difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because we couldn't even eat what we got.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because we developed dysentery.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we were ill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So fortunately, the three weeks-- they put us all together, and they called us by our names, which I understand it never happened in history of Auschwitz, that they would call prisoners by their name.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They usually had numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were not numbered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they called us by our name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All they did it is, like, they smeared us with a paintbrush before we got on those trains.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I, I think the reason was, in case somebody tried to escape, we would be easily spotted, recognized, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
